{
  "stem": "43.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she told me she can hold the-- the two older one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The boy, he was 8 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the little girl was 6 and a 1/2 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and so I-- I couldn't-- I wasn't-- I was laying, and they-- they took me out and lay me in the-- in a place, like in a-- I don't know how to say.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]-- where straw over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know how to-- so you understand?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you are a big girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- and-- and she came, Nadia, and she took away the two children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was near three days they didn't took me to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was swollen in the eye-- and black and blue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After three-- after three days, they took me to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I came to the work, and I-- and I was already to the people-- we was over there near 70-- 70 Yiddish-- mostly women-- the two men was though-- and rest, all of us was woman-- what they got also farms.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I start, what shall I do to take out?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know the ghetto-- every day, maybe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they will kill them all in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to take out the-- the-- the-- the little boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I didn't know what to-- what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when we was in the night, we were sleeping by our little straw over there-- the all 70 over there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked my neighbor near me in the night, what shall we do?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What-- how can I take out from the ghetto the-- the-- the child?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she told me, you know, you talk to the-- in [NON-ENGLISH] to-- and the [NON-ENGLISH] took care a Polish-- a-- a Pollack-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was very nice man.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
